The goal of this research study is to learn how opioid medications (medications that are used to manage pain) are handled by the parents and/or caregivers of patients who are 18 years or younger.

 This includes information on how opioids are stored, used, and disposed of.

 This is an investigational study.

 Up to 150 participants will be enrolled in this study.

 All will take part at MD Anderson.

